flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 30: Cross-Vendor Category Emergence Hourly Pipeline

  Cron[Hourly CRON]
  Read[Read order_items aggregates by category]
  Compute[Compute category_velocity_score\nand vendor_count]
  PrivacyGate{vendor_count >= 3?}

  Publish[Publish aggregate category signal]
  Persist[(Write category_velocity table)]
  Cache[Redis cache TTL 1h]
  FeatureInject[Inject as GBR feature #13\ncategory_velocity_score]

  Suppress[Suppress category aggregate output\nfor privacy]
  Fallback[Fallback to vendor-local signals only\nfor affected categories]

  InternalOnly[Internal-only module\nNo public endpoint]

  Cron --> Read --> Compute --> PrivacyGate

  PrivacyGate -- Yes --> Publish --> Persist --> Cache --> FeatureInject
  PrivacyGate -- No --> Suppress --> Fallback

  Publish --> InternalOnly
  Suppress --> InternalOnly
